		<title>狗狗聞到「雨味」竟會興奮？原來氣味裡藏著牠的快樂記憶</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/09/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e8%81%9e%e5%88%b0%e3%80%8c%e9%9b%a8%e5%91%b3%e3%80%8d%e7%ab%9f%e6%9c%83%e8%88%88%e5%a5%ae%ef%bc%9f%e5%8e%9f%e4%be%86%e6%b0%a3%e5%91%b3%e8%a3%a1%e8%97%8f%e8%91%97%e7%89%a0%e7%9a%84/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
